Automation Testing

UI Testing: Selenium is used and the language is python with framework (Pytest)
1-login with valid/invalid credentials.
2-Creating a new item (e.g., a todo/user).
3-Editing an existing item.
4-Deleting an item.
5-Asserting presence of expected data after actions.
with positive and negative test cases


APIs Testing : REST-assured is used to test the APIs and the language is python with the framework (Pytest)
1-POST /login
2-GET /items
3-POST /items
4-PUT /items/:id
5-DELETE /items/:id
with positive and negative test cases



Run The tests:

UI testing: tests/ui_test.py should be run
APIs testing: tests/apis_test.py should be run


